   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject Two Hundred HE THAT HAS THE SON HAS LIFE Scripture: 1 John 5:11-13 The Son of God is God in another form The Son of God is Jesus Christ.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Jesus Christ is God come as a man in order to save man.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The Son of God is God made manifest to man.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>God s life is in the Son of God God is in His Son, so God s life is also in the Son.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The life that is in the Son of God is the eternal life.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>He that has the Son of God has life Life is within the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>If man wants to obtain life, he must receive the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Once man receives the Son of God, he has God and also the life of God.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>The proof of having life 1 John 5:12 says, He that hath the Son hath the life.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>The proof that someone has obtained life is that his living has changed.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Describe how once a man receives the Lord, his life is changed.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>How to obtain the Son of God Confess that you do not have God s life.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Believe in the Son of God.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>To believe means to receive the Son of God as Savior with our heart and our spirit.</S>
   </TEXT>
